================================================================================
                   ntop - A top-like Erlang node monitoring tool
================================================================================

Ntop is a tool which shows information about a remote Erlang node in a way which
is similar to unix 'top'. It needs (at least) Cecho 0.3.0 
(http://www.github.com/mazenharake/cecho) to run. See the section "Usage" to see
what commands that are supported.

